{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_01","textHome":"你好！我是矢宵鹿乃子！未来想从事的职业，@是时装设计师！总有一天，我的衣服会出现在@巴黎时装周之类的……诶？不是很好嘛！@目标很高吧！这世上，谁知道会发生什么呀！@你看，我都成为魔法少女了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_18","textHome":"这就是我所有设计中最杰出的作品！怎么样？@看不见吗？这个呀，是只有拥有纯洁心灵的人@才能看到的哦～好啦，快舍弃邪念！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_19","textHome":"怎么样怎么样！@我飞速进步的才能，永无止境！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_20","textHome":"想象更加清晰了！这就是觉醒吗！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_21","textHome":"现在头脑的灵活程度……让我想想……@就像灯亮了的感觉吧，稀松平常。@就是说还是普普通通一般般的程度啦。@嗯，希望它再灵光一些！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":400}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_22","textHome":"嗯！来了来了！脑海中仿佛有一盏水晶吊灯，@又像是玻璃珠一般在回旋。@我的身体里有一个自己在翩翩起舞！@感觉设计灵感就要喷涌而出！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_23","textHome":"从未有过的清明！有如太阳般闪亮！@紫外线般的穿透力！如此机智灵动！@以现在的状态，就算是颠覆历史、划时代的@服装我也能……快、快给我笔和纸！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_24","textHome":"哦，你来啦——@今天穿的很不错呀！很适合你哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_25","textHome":"早晨的仪容仪表很重要，所以我想要有充裕的@梳洗时间。嘛，但毕竟只是愿望……@所以头发还是乱蓬蓬的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_26","textHome":"我的便当，和父亲的是一样的哦。@都是母亲做的。我都有点惭愧了……@真的非常感谢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":400}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_27","textHome":"对了！回家路上去那家店看看吧！@有双鞋子我好喜欢。因为知道不可能买下来，@所以只好常常去看！就一直盯着～盯着看！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_03","textHome":"对不起，父亲母亲！请再给我一些时间！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_28","textHome":"……啊！思考服装设计转眼都这个时间了！@糟糕……作业还没做呢……都这会儿了……@嗯，总之先睡吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_29","textHome":"我一直都随身带着纸和笔。@有了灵感就立即写下来！@嗯？这张纸？当然是传单的背面啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_30","textHome":"我不想放弃梦想……因为人生只有一次……@所以，就只能下定决心勇往直前了吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_31","textHome":"这个时候……果然还是气势最重要！@只能打起精神去做了吧！@不要小看工厂家的女儿哦～！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_32","textHome":"这里聚集了这么多人，我就没办法隐藏自己@超凡脱俗的品位了呢！哎呀，真是伤脑筋……@太过显眼会被盯上的吧……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":400}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_33","textHome":"只要在街上看到可爱的衣服，@我就会喜欢到喘不上气！@这已经算是恋爱了吧？@也就是说，我是个多情的女子？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_34","textHome":"我想到了！新的动物花纹。@名字就叫……紫胸佛法僧纹！@这个，是不是很漂亮……诶？想象不出来？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":400}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_35","textHome":"一般说起粉色衣服，都会感觉很可爱吧？@但是，如果再一听是鲑鱼粉，@突然就感觉有鱼腥味了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_36","textHome":"那是什么！好可爱！那件衣服，在哪买的！？@快告诉我告诉我！……诶，对谁都这么打听？@那是因为我好学啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_37","textHome":"总是会有那种不知如何是好的事情对吧……@遇到这种事，我还是会努力逼自己想想@「到底该如何是好呢」……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":400}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_04","textHome":"……不行了……我的心都要碎了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":400}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_38","textHome":"我的父亲，从事机械零部件的精密加工。@他做的零部件非常非常完美！@就算是造火箭也能用的那种！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_39","textHome":"看了我的设计图，大家的反应都很生硬呢。@这也没办法……因为大家都沉浸在感动中嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3001_00_40","textHome":"模拟非常顺利！之后只要像这样，@在人生道路上一路径直向前，@终有一天，我会走上属于自己的T台！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":300100,"motion":200}]}],"group_33"